Aim for Greece Is Success Not Insolvency, EU’s Reichenbach Says

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-09-15T05:22:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/aim-for-greece-is-success-not-insolvency-eu-s-reichenbach-says.html
Horst Reichenbach, who heads a
European Union task force helping  Greece  with privatization and
modernizing its bureaucracy, said he doesn’t see himself
becoming the country’s bankruptcy administrator.  “I’ve come here to create success, not to lead Greece into
insolvency,” Reichenbach said in an interview on  Germany ’s ARD
television today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tony Czuczka at 
 aczuczka@bloomberg.net  